content: Hi, I am Gaurav. I am currently working at Persistent Systems, as a Software Engineer. I am graduated from Savitribai Phule Pune University (BE in Computer Science) in June 2019. I was also an apprentice at Persistent Systems for six months, where i worked on Convolutional Neural Networks and other techniques in Machine Learning and Deep Learning.
